Class LegacyLayout.LegacyRangeTombstone

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.cassandra.db.LegacyLayout.LegacyRangeTombstone

    public static class LegacyLayout.LegacyRangeTombstone
extends java.lang.Object
implements LegacyLayout.LegacyAtom
    A legacy range tombstone.

    This is used as a temporary object to facilitate dealing with the legacy format, this is not meant to be optimal.
